{
  "stem": "26022.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know, they probably thought the upper classes of the Jews ate caviar.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he had-- aside from not knowing what happens tomorrow and what happens to his family and-- and-- and then everything was confiscated, and how are we going to meet the expenses, but aside from that, he had a good time, because they tried to teach him how to burglarize, because you're a Jew, you don't know from nothing, and you're going out into a foreign country, and you don't know the language.",
      "word_count": 73
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What are you going to do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they tried to teach him how to attack a lock and how to, you know, survive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He told us these stories afterwards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they had a-- an intercom, because when you do certain things to the toilet, and the people on the lower floor, on the upper floor-- you know, you have sort of a Morse code with the flushes.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they taught him all that, and he never made any use of it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And this is not so funny.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, that's what happened to my father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother and I stayed in the-- that was one floor of a two-family villa.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we stayed there for a while and then we got-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] no, not yet.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We stayed there for over a year, because when my father was finally released, with nothing pending against him, the firm was gone by then, because this nice [SPEAKING GERMAN] thought the boss sits there, has a mistress, makes phone calls, and takes money.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so all the money was exhausted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Much of the outstanding money was never brought in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He didn't have the faintest idea of production or distribution or business as such.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
